Rating: 3
I will definitely make this again. I made a few changes I would also make again. I used light sour cream instead of yogurt. I baked all of it in one decorative greased and floured bundt pan. This added about 10 minutes baking time. I had 3 layers of batter with the streusel in between. Like other reviewers I found it to be moist and flavorful. I think the sour cream helped. The presentation was great as I put it on a nice large plate and dusted it with powdered sugar.

