I used fat free plain yogurt to see how it would work. I made one loaf using 2 eggs and added chopped roasted nuts to the streusel mix. The cake was moist and tender but not as flavorful as I'd hoped. I don't think the apples added anything but chopping time. Next time I will add cinnamon and more vanilla to the cake base.

